{
  "stem": "14060.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember very clearly when we were told by one of the railway employees that this train came from, from Athens carrying Jews from Crete.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I literally saw those trains going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lit-- You saw the trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Presumably, you couldn't see any people because there were no windows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because look, in one-- imagine yourself there is a alternate to a railway station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in the-- the railway station was not very far where we lived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't go out to the platform, because obviously, they didn't allow anybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew that there was a train of some importance going through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But next to the railway station there was a clearing where, where the railway lines were running.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was within maybe 40, 50 meters from where the railway lines were running.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But obviously, these tracks and this tiny little hole, and God knows how long those people have been already on the train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not leaning out on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all I'm trying to say is that we knew when-- which later became known as deportations-- these transports were going through our town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, even I, I remember very clearly when the African campaign of Roma was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Similarly, the sand painted tanks and armored vehicles on train tracks were going through our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You see, it was a junction from Germany, Austria down to the south.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, so we were none the wiser what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We certainly didn't know what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I told you about the SS brigades who went from our town as volunteers and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
